    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready for something truly special? This gem is in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! You'll be hard-pressed to find a flaw, inside or out. The interior is fresh and spotless, the exterior gleams with no visible blemishes, and everything runs and functions exactly as it should. This is the kind of car you'd be proud to show off on day one and every day after. If you've been waiting for the right car, your wait is over!",
